      <scopecontent id="aspace_05997042834302b8de0e1f32b2baa4a6">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of a typed letter from Albert Tate, Jr., founding editor of the Yale Freshman Weekly, to Charles H. Long, Jr. The letter documents the history of the publication, which appeared from 1938-1943.</p>  
